      • enableThreadCpuTimeMeasurement

        public static final boolean enableThreadCpuTimeMeasurement()
        Tries to enable CPU time measurement for threads. Not all JVMs support this feature.
        Returns:
        true if the JVM supports time measurement for threads and the feature could be enabled, false otherwise.

      • getThreadCpuTime
